<BaseLayout
  title="Costco Hot Dog Nutrition: 570 Cal, 24g Protein, 33g Fat (2026)"
  description="Complete Costco hot dog nutrition facts: 570 calories, 24g protein, 33g fat, 46g carbs, 1,700mg sodium. See the macro breakdown, health context, and dietary tips. Updated 2026."
