  publishedAt="2026-04-29"
  modifiedAt="2026-05-08"
  faqData={[{"question":"Is a Costco hot dog healthy?","answer":"It can fit a balanced diet occasionally, but sodium and saturated fat are the main limits for frequent intake."},{"question":"What are Costco hot dog macros?","answer":"A typical hot dog with bun has about 24g protein, 33g fat, and 46g carbs, with sodium around 1,700mg."},{"question":"Is sodium the biggest concern?","answer":"For most people, yes. One serving can cover a large share of a full-day sodium limit."},{"question":"Where can I see exact calories with and without bun?","answer":"See the dedicated calories page for side-by-side values and yearly comparison: /hot-dog/calories/."}]}
